Text:
As allready mentioned TCR number on top of screen, but still a great copy.
Yet another British gangland romp with loads of violents and swearing. PLenty of well know British stars from the world of soaps. If you enjoyed the Football Factory and the like!! yer luv this.

the only bad thing about this movie is the HUGE timing mark at the top....kinda like the one from the early screener of The Bourne Ultimatum.
Just giving a heads up on quality.
Other than the timing mark its awesome quality.
Is there any chance we could get a seed on this, most poeple are at 99.8%- it would only take a short time!!!
